u như hồng, thuỷ như không) - 長相思其一（橋如虹，水如空）</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%A5c-Du/author-6xOAUbKdWiBr-eAAn9zXQQ">Lục Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/Tu%C3%BD-ca-h%C3%A0nh/poem-6y9rj-YrWsH2nTdU8zPseA">Tuý ca hành - 醉歌行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Thi%C3%AAn-Du/author-t5zNl0R6g-15oc9Dd33Eqg">Hồ Thiên Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/Xu%C3%A2n-s%E1%BA%A7u-thi-hi%E1%BB%87u-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Xuy%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%AD/poem-b0lVaHG5wN40Hu-ickJ1_g">Xuân sầu thi hiệu Ngọc Xuyên Tử - 春愁詩效玉川子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BA%BFt-Qu%C3%BD-Tuy%C3%AAn/author-HlAsEr3qGyMOUeGTRRdhhQ">Tiết Quý Tuyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0ng-Minh/X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-M%C3%B4n-d%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BA%A1c/poem-Sw2zpf6RJG6jx6b985vnFA">Xương Môn dạ bạc - 閶門夜泊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-Tr%C6%B0ng-Minh/author-xHa000oq0fYTe8iRr83EKg">Văn Trưng Minh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
